---
title: Firey Mapo-Style Crispy Tofu with Jasmine Rice and Sesame-Roasted Broccoli
description: This dinner brings the heat of chilis and Szechwan peppercorns to amp up this tofu dish! Roasted broccoli and sesame-studded jasmine rice help to temper the spice!
